text: ate lokam vica ko'i ajiha hai jihara kahida hai ki asim alaha te imana li'a'e ate phira jadom' alaha de raha vica usa nu presana kita janda hai tam uha lokam de presana hona nu alaha di saza varaga samajha lainda hai ate jekara tuhade raba valom ko'i madada a jave tam uha kahinage ki asim tam tuhade nala si. Ki alaha usa tom cagi tar'ham janu nahim jihara lokam de dilam vica hai
